						<summary>

						<p>On the stone door-frame of the village gate.</p>						

						<p>Circa 16th century.</p>						

						<p>The inscription which is damaged mentions <hi rend="italic">Mahāmaṇḍalēśvara</hi> Narasarājayya. It seems to record a gift of land. </p>						

